data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the Luckey Ranch subdivision! This charming one story traditional home, nestled in the desirable Medina Valley School District.  Literally just a block away walking distance to the gigantic park and Luckey Ranch Elementary!  This is one of the most favored layouts with a great open floorplan design where the kitchen opens up in to the living room and all three bedrooms are around down the hallway.  Kitchen has granite counters and dark cabinets along with stainless steel appliances!  Tiled flooring throughout except for the bedrooms for very simple maintenance and high durability.  The master suite is a retreat of tranquility with its spacious layout along with a stand up shower and separate tub set up as well. Step outside into the backyard, a private oasis where memories are waiting to be made. Whether you're hosting a summer barbecue or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars.  House has some minor wear and tear on the baseboards and carpets but repairs can be done and are negotiable at buyer's request.
